    <h1>Password Help</h1>
    <p>If you're experiencing issues logging in or think you've forgotten your password, follow these steps:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Try using the "Forgot Password" option on the login screen.</li>
      <li>Ensure Caps Lock is off.</li>
      <li>If you're using a temporary password, make sure it hasn't expired.</li>
      <li>Clear your browser cache and cookies and try again.</li>
      <li>If prompted to change your password, ensure it meets complexity requirements.</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/account-billing/how-to-reset-your-microsoft-account-password-eff4f067-5042-c1a3-fe72-b04d60556c37" class="button" target="_blank">
      Reset Microsoft Password
